3Ô∏è‚É£ Endpoint :
```
        private readonly ApplicationDbContext _context;
        private List<string> _allowExtension = new List<string>() { ".jpg", ".png" };
        private long _MaxSize = 1024;
        public MoviesController(ApplicationDbContext context)
        {
            _context = context;
        }
 [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Create([FromForm]MovieDTO dTO)
        {
            if (dTO == null) return NotFound("Null Object");
            if (!_allowExtension.Contains(Path.GetExtension(dTO.Poster.FileName.ToLower())))
                return BadRequest("Extention Must be Jpg Or Png");
            if(dTO.Poster.FileName.Length>_MaxSize)
                return BadRequest("Extention Must be 1MB");

            using var data= new MemoryStream();
            await dTO.Poster.CopyToAsync(data);
            var movie = new Movie()
            {
                Title = dTO.Title,
                Year = dTO.Year,
                GenreId = dTO.GenreId,
                Poster = data.ToArray(),
                Rate = dTO.Rate,
                StoreLine = dTO.StoreLine,
            };
            await _context.Movies.AddAsync(movie);
            await _context.SaveChangesAsync();
            return Ok(movie);
        } 
```
